So I went late.

429
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:20,290
You know who I saw today?

430
00:23:21,720 --> 00:23:22,180
Who?

431
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,220
Tan Siting.

432
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:26,290
Is that so?

433
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:30,570
Picking the venue,
choosing the wedding dress.

434
00:23:31,280 --> 00:23:32,740
She was there both times.

435
00:23:34,070 --> 00:23:35,460
Is she close to Yan?

436
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:38,260
Or is it because of you?

437
00:23:39,520 --> 00:23:40,050
Mom,

438
00:23:40,830 --> 00:23:42,020
